window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>From the <i>New York Times</i> bestselling author of the <i>Shades of Magic</i> series, <i>The Near Witch</i>, and <i>The Archived</i>, comes \"Warm Up,\" a Tor.com Original prequel story to V. E. Schwab's<i> Vicious</i></b> <br><br>It's been 297 days since David died--and came back. He may have survived the avalanche, but the aftermath has been far worse. His wife moved out, taking his son with her, and a devastated David hasn't left his house since, terrified of the mysterious new power that followed him home from the ill-fated expedition. After months in seclusion, David's ready for a fresh start, and ventures out, determined to keep his power in check. <br><br>But David's power isn't the one he needs to worry about.</p>"; 
